.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.TH search 1  "search " 
.SH NAME
search \- Full\-text search across notes and context
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBsearch\fR [\fB\-\-note\fR] [\fB\-\-context\fR] [\fB\-\-semantic\fR] [\fB\-\-limit\fR] [\fB\-\-lang\fR] [\fB\-\-author\fR] [\fB\-\-collection\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fIQUERY\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Full\-text search across notes and context
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-note\fR \fI<NOTE>\fR
Search only in notes
.TP
\fB\-\-context\fR \fI<CONTEXT>\fR
Search only in context
.TP
\fB\-\-semantic\fR
Use semantic search (vector embeddings)
.TP
\fB\-\-limit\fR \fI<LIMIT>\fR [default: 20]
Maximum results to return (default: 20)
.TP
\fB\-\-lang\fR \fI<LANG>\fR
Filter by language (swift, rust, typescript, python)
.TP
\fB\-\-author\fR \fI<AUTHOR>\fR
Filter by author (user, agent, or any identifier)
.TP
\fB\-\-collection\fR \fI<COLLECTION>\fR
Filter by collection
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
[\fIQUERY\fR]
Search query (searches both notes and context)
